All right, here I go.

16:47.140 --> 16:52.810
<i>Go down on this ice crossing</i>
<i>and splash my way across it.</i>

17:01.520 --> 17:04.989
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Deep in the thawing</i>
<i>wilderness...</i>

17:04.991 --> 17:07.358
(Shifts gear)

17:07.360 --> 17:09.494
All right, here I go.

17:09.496 --> 17:13.798
<i>Go down on this ice crossing</i>
<i>and splash my way across it.</i>

17:13.800 --> 17:17.869
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Darrell Ward's rolling</i>
<i>the dice.</i>

17:19.605 --> 17:22.473
<i>Darrell:</i>
<i>My first is crossing</i>
<i>in 50 degrees.</i>

