<i>The softening ice can barely</i>
<i>withstand the pressure</i>

18:34.681 --> 18:36.481
<i>from Darrell's 20 tonne rig.</i>

18:36.483 --> 18:39.984
Darrell:
Looks bad up there.

18:39.986 --> 18:44.655
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Causing cracks to spring up</i>
<i>all around.</i>

18:54.233 --> 18:56.734
