Just a little farther.

18:56.736 --> 19:06.844
♪

19:06.846 --> 19:12.316
♪

19:12.318 --> 19:14.685
That's how we do it!

19:14.687 --> 19:18.656
<i>Successfully sailed</i>
<i>another crossing.</i>

19:18.658 --> 19:21.259
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Darrell reaches mud-soaked</i>
<i>land.</i>

19:21.261 --> 19:24.529
