19:24.531 --> 19:28.266
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Surviving the crossing</i>
<i>and proving once again,</i>

19:28.268 --> 19:32.503
<i>nothing can keep</i>
<i>the young company down.</i>

19:32.505 --> 19:34.338
<i>Darrell:</i>
<i>So, I made it in to Big Trout.</i>

19:34.340 --> 19:37.308
<i>Another load for the books.</i>

