Lots of loads.

19:42.916 --> 19:45.249
<i>So, I'm gonna get in here,</i>

19:45.251 --> 19:50.121
<i>and then I'm gonna head back</i>
<i>towards Winnipeg.</i>

19:50.123 --> 19:54.692
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>As Darrell pulls up</i>
<i>to the offload...</i>

19:54.694 --> 19:57.061
