This is it.

20:53.686 --> 20:57.588
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>And so far, it's a tough slog.</i>

20:58.657 --> 21:03.361
♪

21:03.363 --> 21:06.464
<i>Todd:</i>
<i>Give her everything she's got,</i>
<i>believe that.</i>

21:06.466 --> 21:08.499
<i>And then some.</i>

