<i>This is an old machine,</i>
<i>I don't want to break it.</i>

21:13.373 --> 21:15.039
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>But now...</i>

21:15.041 --> 21:17.308
Todd:
We got some hills to go over.

21:17.310 --> 21:18.976
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>The convoy has got to pass over</i>

21:18.978 --> 21:22.113
<i>a peninsula littered</i>
<i>with frozen hills.</i>

21:36.128 --> 21:37.695
<i>Wee hoo!</i>

21:37.697 --> 21:39.430
<i>Whoa!</i>

21:40.732 --> 21:42.133
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>With a light load...</i>

21:45.237 --> 21:48.639
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Lisa makes it with ease.</i>

21:50.042 --> 21:52.610
Todd:
I don't know how this thing
is gonna do either.

21:52.612 --> 21:56.213
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Now, pulling a 17 tonne</i>
<i>excavator,</i>

21:56.215 --> 21:58.049
<i>it's Todd's turn.</i>

22:19.805 --> 22:21.539
(Bleep)!

22:25.344 --> 22:27.144
