22:36.723 --> 22:38.422
(Engine revving)

22:38.424 --> 22:40.925
<i>Todd:</i>
<i>Come on!</i>

22:40.927 --> 22:43.260
Come on you son of a bitch!

22:44.463 --> 22:46.330
Going up.

22:58.577 --> 23:02.646
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>On the edge</i>
<i>of the Hudson Bay...</i>

23:02.648 --> 23:07.485
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Todd Dewey's facing</i>
<i>an uphill battle.</i>

23:07.487 --> 23:10.388
<i>Todd:</i>
<i>Come on!</i>

23:10.390 --> 23:13.190
Come on, you son of a bitch!

