23:29.041 --> 23:31.509
(Treads spinning)

23:34.980 --> 23:37.248
(Frustrated grunt)

23:37.250 --> 23:38.883
(Grinding)

23:38.885 --> 23:41.452
Dammit, this is hard.

23:41.454 --> 23:43.888
It's this (bleep) deep snow,
it just buries her.

23:43.890 --> 23:46.023
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>To get the added power</i>
<i>he needs,</i>

23:46.025 --> 23:49.226
<i>Todd calls in the emergency</i>
<i>driver in the excavator</i>

23:49.228 --> 23:51.395
<i>to help push him over.</i>

23:56.401 --> 23:58.469
(Engine revving)

24:02.007 --> 24:03.574
Todd:
Come on!

24:05.043 --> 24:07.445
(Engine revving)

24:11.316 --> 24:12.817
Holy smokes!

24:14.654 --> 24:18.189
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Todd's made it to the other</i>
<i>side,</i>

24:18.191 --> 24:21.258
<i>but now, (machine groaning)</i>

