25:13.211 --> 25:15.713
<i>Come on, girl!</i>

25:15.715 --> 25:17.448
(Metal creaking)

25:19.417 --> 25:21.785
(Engine revving)

25:31.429 --> 25:34.331
<i>Todd:</i>
<i>There she goes.</i>

25:34.333 --> 25:37.501
Whoo hoo hoo!

25:37.503 --> 25:41.939
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>The convoy's back in business.</i>

25:41.941 --> 25:44.341
<i>Todd:</i>
<i>(Howling)</i>

25:50.148 --> 25:53.717
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>But 25 miles of rugged</i>
<i>tundra and frozen sea</i>

25:53.719 --> 25:55.686
<i>still loom ahead.</i>

26:01.092 --> 26:02.860
I just hope this engine
has what it takes

26:02.862 --> 26:05.329
