26:06.631 --> 26:10.334
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>While Todd and Lisa</i>
<i>push further north,</i>

26:10.336 --> 26:14.438
<i>250 miles to the south...</i>

26:14.440 --> 26:16.173
<i>Mike:</i>
<i>Keep them tires down, baby.</i>

26:16.175 --> 26:18.442
Come on. Come on!

26:18.444 --> 26:21.645
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Polar newcomer Mike Simmons...</i>

26:21.647 --> 26:24.148
<i>Mike:</i>
<i>How's the road looking ahead,</i>
<i>Art?</i>

26:24.150 --> 26:26.483
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>...and veteran Art Burke...</i>

26:26.485 --> 26:27.952
(Bleep)

26:29.387 --> 26:33.357
Art:
All in all, totally (bleep).

