26:39.699 --> 26:42.232
<i>Art:</i>
<i>I can't see the road at all,</i>
<i>b'y.</i>

26:42.234 --> 26:48.138
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>But a recent snowfall has</i>
<i>hidden the bumps and potholes</i>
<i>below.</i>

26:48.140 --> 26:49.773
<i>Art:</i>
<i>Hang on.</i>

26:49.775 --> 26:52.109
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Wreaking havoc for the only</i>
<i>two drivers</i>

26:52.111 --> 26:54.945
<i>on the remote private trail.</i>

26:54.947 --> 26:56.847
Holy shit.

26:56.849 --> 26:59.283
<i>Art:</i>
<i>Hopefully, we'll make it.</i>

26:59.285 --> 27:01.852
Mike:
Just a little bit to go.

27:09.694 --> 27:11.061
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Finally...</i>

27:11.063 --> 27:14.231
Art:
