Mike:
Hey, my brother.

27:45.564 --> 27:47.398
(Laughing)

27:47.400 --> 27:48.565
Good to see ya, b'y.

27:48.567 --> 27:50.300
(Bleep), that's some surreal
(bleep) right there, eh?

27:50.302 --> 27:51.535
Nothing around?

27:51.537 --> 27:52.836
<i>Art:</i>
<i>When it comes to the ice road,</i>

27:52.838 --> 27:55.472
I would say that some of the
best drivers in North America

27:55.474 --> 27:57.641
drive them (bleep) ice roads,
