27:57.643 --> 27:59.476
And he got a chance to join us.

27:59.478 --> 28:00.711
I'm outta here, b'y.

28:00.713 --> 28:02.379
Okay, I'll-
Both: I'll see you in Winnipeg.

28:02.381 --> 28:05.215
Art:
You be safe.

28:05.217 --> 28:08.686
<i>Narrator:</i>
<i>Looking to burn through the</i>
